me.lucko.helper.gson

Interface GsonSerializable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Hologram
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlockPosition, BlockRegion, ChunkPosition, ChunkRegion, Direction, Point, Position, Region

    public interface GsonSerializable
    An object which can be serialized to JSON.

    Classes which implement this interface should also implement a static "deserialize" method, accepting JsonElement as the only parameter.
